{"tid":872861,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本：寧願尋求對話和承諾，多於跟隨美國對中國商品加徵關稅","createTime":"2018-10-23T04:32:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-28T02:48:30.000Z","uid":91914,"like":6,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b6e3464157e87bee287beb899e25f268ae2b5e59","tid":872861,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T04:32:52.000Z","msg":"日本首相安倍晉三將於周四至周六（25至27日）訪問中國。在中美貿易摩擦持續之際，作為美國長期盟友的日本，將有約500名商界領袖隨同安倍訪華。 <br />\n<br />\n日本一名匿名官員周一（22日）透露有關消息，指雙方考慮在泰國等第三國的基礎建設及經濟項目上合作。中日的貿易額達3000億美元（約2.34萬億港元），比美日的2000億美元（1.56萬億港元）更多，其中日本汽車和食品等在中國市場佔有重要地位。該官員表示，日企與歐美企業一樣關注中國在貿易和技術方面的行為，但日方寧願尋求對話和承諾，多於跟隨美國對中國商品加徵關稅，並強調「我們不希望中美貿易摩擦損害國際體制」。 <br />\n<br />\n該官員亦表示，中日領導人亦會討論北韓議題，日方希望北韓處理日本人被綁架的問題，以改善日朝關係。他指出，中日同意繼續向北韓施壓，包括打擊在海上轉移以規避禁運原油制裁的行為。"},{"pid":"a7b2c9398ddc33be06755e304bc0fe3aed69e094","tid":872861,"uid":166785,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T04:34:12.000Z","msg":"去前又拜拜神社先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f79c1cf2646f63fada6cbdba75008b79d17d6d8","tid":872861,"uid":58552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T04:35:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/23/123517_9ec328a6280c94374298512d20232b94.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F23%2F123517_9ec328a6280c94374298512d20232b94.png&h=bc45b304&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f42e1ce954273e56d891940961d9515b42ba5c37","tid":872861,"uid":51057,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T04:42:39.000Z","msg":"同支那講承諾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"511d19b36bbf688d520f71e7a5b4b046ef980edf","tid":872861,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T04:44:41.000Z","msg":"日本跨黨派議員參拜靖國神社 18/10<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/869884\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/869884</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"01dcfa31291f9ac2ba5e9a7a26788398e6ef415b","tid":872861,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T04:46:02.000Z","msg":"日本都深知畀支那發圍 如果打仗無後果<br />\n第一個打就一定係日本"},{"pid":"7aaffd7f6ca67e490e97f10cc30665935b9de158","tid":872861,"uid":45368,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T05:02:48.000Z","msg":"日本有自己思想，唔盲目跟蹤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83e5740bc0addeff1cff59d0676d0db1c9429f90","tid":872861,"uid":132038,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T05:25:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e2a618aee10146ec7bcf48d03feb697928fb93ce","tid":872861,"uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T05:28:57.000Z","msg":"幾時去靖國神社尋求英靈對話？"},{"pid":"7ae817ad87f76103616eba8fbf43d3e60a27b88e","tid":872861,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7aaffd7f6ca67e490e97f10cc30665935b9de158","tid":872861,"uid":45368,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T05:02:48.000Z","msg":"日本有自己思想，唔盲目跟蹤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T05:49:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4f1fba98557dd59d616bcf5ecb7957d8a2931cb","tid":872861,"uid":103513,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T07:13:27.000Z","msg":"又想食兩家茶禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n支那個茶禮有毒架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59fd184ca8baab183d0ab32c7bb5224debc1a20b","tid":872861,"uid":193026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T07:16:04.000Z","msg":"正一ゆとり世代<img src=\"/assets/fa